name: What'sOnTCL

”Alexa, open What's On T. C. L.”
”Alexa, ask What's On T. C. L. for the latest talk”
”Alexa, start What's On T. C. L.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: what's on t. c. l.
des: Here's what is coming up today on Twin Cities Live, which airs weekdays at 3 p.m. on 5 Eyewitness News, the ABC affiliate in the Twin Cities. You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." The message will loop until you say "Alexa, stop.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
